14 WHEREAS, the Georgia Nurses Association supports and advocates for the many ways in
15 which registered nurses of all levels of education and training strive to provide safe and high
16 quality patient care and maps out ways to improve our health care system.
17 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
18 the members of this body recognize February 19, 2025, as Nurses Day at the state capitol and
19 commend the men and women of our nursing workforce for their strength, leadership, and
20 courage in their willingness to find meaning in something greater than themselves.
21 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
22 and directed to make appropriate copies of this resolution available for distribution to the
23 public and the press.
